{"tid":1526082,"cid":1,"subCid":0,"title":"有冇人係屋企靜靜地果時會有幻聽聽到狗車聲","createTime":"2019-09-01T04:12:05.000Z","updateTime":"2019-09-01T04:14:48.000Z","uid":34793,"like":0,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":2,"replies":[{"pid":"04ac8f7931b5ac38edadbb94df498a2515636787","tid":1526082,"uid":34793,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-01T04:12:05.000Z","msg":"同其他手足一樣 會睇下新聞發下夢<br />\n所以呢排個人好nagative 日日又嬲又驚<br />\n最近係房靜靜地 都成日好似聽到狗車聲咁<br />\n開窗聽真啲 又好似冇<br />\n就痴線 有冇巴打都係咁<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"e32d09f5577445e35e7a38cf15d8778af3b0860e","tid":1526082,"uid":169262,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-01T04:14:48.000Z","msg":"901 機場攻略<br />\n麻煩大家用盡所有方法傳開佢<br />\n<br />\n- <span style=\"color: red;\">準時</span>到機場，唔係一點先出門口<br />\n- 衣着同裝備冇任何限制，最緊要保護自己<br />\n- 集合地點：機場巴士總站(暢達路)<br />\n- 測試方法：排隊戰術，見到<span style=\"color: red;\">有隊就排</span>；利用人數優勢，<span style=\"color: red;\">唔好單獨行事</span><br />\n- 唔好同任何遊客有肢體碰撞<br />\n- 去機場：<span style=\"color: red;\">以巴士為優先</span>，機場快線集中係香港同青衣站上車<br />\n- 已經準備左幾套應變方案，根據現場情況<span style=\"color: red;\">隨時轉變</span>，要密切留意住 901 機場 Channel<br />\n<a href=\"http://t.me/stuckwithyou\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=http%3A%2F%2Ft.me%2Fstuckwithyou&d=dE5eED8%2BMjLqHtNzOSR2X6%2BgbAIUXjhk7Wr4LW24j58%3D&h=f1f3f88b\" target=\"_blank\">http://t.me/stuckwithyou</a><br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/P5XusdO.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FP5XusdO.jpg&h=31adcd48&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/cTXKf68.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FcTXKf68.jpg&h=74d57433&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/qAxaV7a.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FqAxaV7a.jpg&h=13c2eb06&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/otZAnNa.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi